    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎来到 Healer Simulator RPG! </strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/5b3a3751a3ba517087904c461d54e971.poster.avif?t=1747478007\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/5b3a3751a3ba517087904c461d54e971.webm?t=1747478007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/5b3a3751a3ba517087904c461d54e971.mp4?t=1747478007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你能帮助生病的居民吗？</strong></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/d73e487f6d1d0cef07309d14be7d7a8a.poster.avif?t=1747478007\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/d73e487f6d1d0cef07309d14be7d7a8a.webm?t=1747478007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/d73e487f6d1d0cef07309d14be7d7a8a.mp4?t=1747478007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你能解开所有谜题吗？</strong></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/8a2ab4b3fd9218a4d736aa4b4a424a20.poster.avif?t=1747478007\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/8a2ab4b3fd9218a4d736aa4b4a424a20.webm?t=1747478007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/8a2ab4b3fd9218a4d736aa4b4a424a20.mp4?t=1747478007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你能击败敌人吗？</strong></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/4df6e782704ece5220ebf761125eab8d.poster.avif?t=1747478007\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/4df6e782704ece5220ebf761125eab8d.webm?t=1747478007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/4df6e782704ece5220ebf761125eab8d.mp4?t=1747478007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>来一探究竟吧！精彩的冒险和奇特的转折在等着你！</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你受伤了。你很痛苦。你感到委屈。</h2></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你跳入了一个传送门……</i></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/b48e6b46da473376bb12d51ed6b22d29.avif?t=1747478007\" width=254 height=254 /></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你醒了过来。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的脖子上挂着一个破碎的护身符。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的记忆消失了……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你面前站着一个女孩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她带着警惕和好奇看着你。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/85a4583f2821853deab8e2d97e01c7e0.avif?t=1747478007\" width=254 height=254 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你感受到力量的觉醒……一种能够治愈他人的力量。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但不能治愈你自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未来会发生什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >答案？还是……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更多的问题？……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>祝你好运！:)</i></strong></p><br>在这个世界中，你是一位拥有治愈魔法的魔法师！<br>你将解开这个世界的谜团，并治愈那些生病、受伤或患有其他心理和身体问题的人。<br>这是<strong>模拟器</strong>，这是<strong>冒险</strong>，这是<strong>RPG</strong>：<br>这是<strong>Healer Simulator RPG</strong>。",
